{"tid":2021133,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)魔宮帝國1-2 街頭霸王","createTime":"2020-05-17T13:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T19:32:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d8262c9842ed6ca315f3831c6ebe9359dd11d098","tid":2021133,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=ef64f875\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=795bb5ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=1460ae71\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/a/a5/Mortal_Kombat_1995_poster.jpg/220px-Mortal_Kombat_1995_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fa5%2FMortal_Kombat_1995_poster.jpg%2F220px-Mortal_Kombat_1995_poster.jpg&h=7e370bc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/p0504223/1403972618-147346230_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fp0504223%2F1403972618-147346230_m.jpg&h=26a9ddc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.位於天地邊沿的魔界向人類挑戰，若這次人界落敗，邪魔立即統治人類世界，淪入萬劫不復之地。為了迎接這項挑戰，保衛人界的雷電之神派出三名正義勇士迎戰，起初還能輕易打敗大魔神的邪魔武士，但當大魔神製造幻像，三人旋即陷入困境，幸得魔界公主相助方能擊敗魔頭，人界才能得以見天日<br />\n<br />\n2.這次說的是天界惡魔要打通陰陽道，這樣一來，能幫助人間勇士的天神亦無計可施，天地格斗大賽的地上一方只有依靠自己的力量，與魔鬼進行一場生死搏鬥。期限無多，凡間的鬥士怎樣才能迅速充實自己的力量呢？<br />\n<br />\n3.經遜將軍擄走了六十三名解放工人為人質，威脅聯軍部隊在七十二小時內交出二十億贖金，聯軍基路上校與甘美將軍查探比遜總部保壘地點企圖救人，卻因記者春麗把事情越弄越複雜...........<br />\n<br />\n10 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 播完再算<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=0ab5b579\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=bc8ccfc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ade97cc8fb6f0a3fd114b7abf39b7f9de4dbb1","tid":2021133,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"[戰略分析]香城ONLINE 527添馬之戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2015261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih